| `internal/monitor/worktree_lock.go` | NEW — lock primitives + walk-up + companion reader |
| `cmd/endless-hook/claude.go` | EDIT — SessionStart (after line 126), PreToolUse (before line 348), SessionEnd (after line 187) |
